1.0.name: wordpress/edit-my-breadcrumb
1.0.description: Edit My Breadcrumb is a plugin for WordPress that allows for breadcrumbs to be added to your page. It is fully customizable for your website needs. There are two options to implement this into your site; web developers can add a function into their theme or it can be automatically added before your content.
